comment.narrative:
The AMAP convened meetings and workshops during the year to address the recommendations arising from the IRR. The terms of reference of the AMAP included: 
Adaptive Management Advisory Panel (AMAP) ToR:
>Review and provide inputs to the formulation of the Adaptive Management Action Plan generated from the IRR;
>Advise whether adaptive management measures should be implemented;
>Provide oversight of the implementation of mitigation and adaptive management measures and review their performance;
>Report findings to the Project Steering Committee; and Identify emerging issues.
